Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.56,0:00:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一集马上要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.07,0:00:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.84,0:00:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.47,0:00:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了寻找突然失踪的奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.31,0:00:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一行人展开漫长的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.67,0:00:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家曾经一起\N度过好多次难关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.34,0:00:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这次大家又要一起\N面对心灵的地狱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.01,0:00:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师加上珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.78,0:00:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.02,0:00:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.35,0:00:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.99,0:00:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.03,0:00:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.00,0:00:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.04,0:00:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.01,0:00:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.32,0:01:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.82,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.00,0:01:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.01,0:01:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.01,0:01:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.96,0:01:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.03,0:01:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.86,0:02:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在还找不到出口吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.43,0:02:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了  会分心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.36,0:02:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早到现在都还没搞定\N马上就要天黑了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛抖个不停啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.94,0:02:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师\N这座森林果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.44,0:02:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不会错了\N一定是妖怪的巢穴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.45,0:02:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  又爆胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.98,0:02:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种没用的废物  扔掉算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.09,0:02:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我妈买给我的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.09,0:02:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一股邪恶的气息…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座森林的主人\N差不多该现身了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.20,0:02:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会出现的会是鬼  还是蛇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.04,0:03:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪快点现身吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么话快说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那边装模作样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我滚出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临我这座可悲的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.37,0:03:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第100话 真实的恶梦\N可悲的森林之役
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你看这妖怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  是蛾天丸同类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.51,0:03:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦?你们认得\N蛾天丸那家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.25,0:03:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是我们族人的耻辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说他跟一些\N低贱的人类狼狈为奸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后居然死在半妖的手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这把刀还真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.40,0:03:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚说的半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.77,0:04:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时那样的结果\N我还正觉得无趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有妖怪血的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只死妖虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.89,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想帮蛾天丸报仇的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天本大爷\N会很兴奋的奉陪到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮蛾天丸报仇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别说笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.83,0:04:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种邪魔歪道  死了活该
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会理他那些闲事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱怎么说都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.60,0:04:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你们这些飞蛾死虫怪\N也一样没有好感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.11,0:04:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.05,0:04:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.72,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.99,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是什么呀\N啊  啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.79,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直冲进身体里面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.80,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力气…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐被吸走…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.87,0:05:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.57,0:05:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.37,0:05:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连铁碎牙也不管用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吃人类的鲜血的\N是那些邪魔歪道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们全族的人\N一向吃的都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧的心\N还有脆弱的灵魂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.89,0:05:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒  别被控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.54,0:05:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要坚强一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在再大声都没用  臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本就听不见你的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  回答我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.68,0:05:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用等到天亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那些分身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会把他们的\N灵魂跟肉体吃个精光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.93,0:06:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤…试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.37,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不管用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子只有打败这个妖怪\N才能解开法术吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.65,0:06:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在连续不断的恶梦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些隐藏在内心深处的\N恐惧跟绝望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.79,0:06:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都给我唤醒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.98,0:06:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧  琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子连云母都比不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他应该还不能应付实战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不这么认为  爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得琥珀\N耍链条耍得很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么说的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.07,0:07:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一琥珀有什么危险\N还有我跟着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.72,0:07:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…可怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我好害怕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了  姐姐在这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快  愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.82,0:08:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样出来散散心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那些什么痛苦烦恼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就都把它忘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.82,0:08:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦心师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.82,0:08:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有看见\N我爸爸在这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.06,0:08:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦心师父?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.56,0:08:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亲生父亲告诉我\N恐怕要跟你来世再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来世再见…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候恐怕已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.81,0:08:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.80,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  爸爸\N我捡了这么多松果回来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.27,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.93,0:09:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么啦  草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蚋在里面耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有点怪怪的\N我觉得很不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊  草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.60,0:09:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股瘴气是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太  你快跑  快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太  振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么声音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不可以过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续受苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受完苦之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有永无止尽的绝望\N等着你们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.35,0:10:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地 慢慢地\N品尝那些恐怖的滋味吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死妖怪\N你到底对他们做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过让他们做做梦而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们做梦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管人也好 妖怪也罢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.43,0:10:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏在内心深处的那种恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.43,0:10:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会借着梦境\N变得非常非常的具体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这些东西\N就是我们的饵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.77,0:10:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这死妖怪简直乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在立刻放了戈薇他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你这只半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得出来\N你开始感到恐惧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.95,0:11:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不跟大家成群结队的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.29,0:11:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本是胆小又没用的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.79,0:11:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算剩下我一个\N我也照样能打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.16,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.30,0:11:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然拿我的同伴当成你的饵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不能忍受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那边逞英雄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.91,0:11:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最害怕最难忍受的恐惧\N我也会一并吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你还能威风多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招吧  风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呸  光会用一张嘴说说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.51,0:11:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样就算赢了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我这条命没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不断帮我\N啃食他们的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.68,0:12:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有肉体的分身\N全都会复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.02,0:12:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候就是你的死期了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.86,0:12:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等着成为\N你那些同伴的饵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而到那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.03,0:12:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也才有机会\N真正摆脱孤独的恐惧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.54,0:12:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫茧居然没有消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.15,0:12:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可恶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个浑蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.58,0:13:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于办到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人打败妖怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打败妖怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次爸爸一定会\N夸奖我做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.92,0:13:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是姐姐你的错哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你没有夸奖我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦心师父  放了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.51,0:14:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那个风穴\N现在已经用到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后你哪里都去不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.65,0:14:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定把奈落找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只差一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  你怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.87,0:14:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们全都不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.02,0:14:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会…\N我根本没打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师\N你就那么想帮我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.06,0:15:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了帮我\N牺牲同伴的性命也在所不惜吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切全部都是你的杰作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你对我爷爷\N下了这个风穴诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜啊  救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.82,0:15:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在上课的时候做梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么啦  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.53,0:15:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少看到你上课打瞌睡耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚睡得还真熟哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为太过用功念书啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为这种事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.05,0:15:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续待在这里会有危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞刃血爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.33,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的韧性跑到哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会被梦境给侵蚀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这么脆弱的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.75,0:16:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的看错你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你就这样放弃自己的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.29,0:16:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要一个人\N自己去击败奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候你可不要\N跟在后面哭哭啼啼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点醒过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.14,0:16:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可以\N让那只飞蛾怪吃掉你的心灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.69,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.39,0:17:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一向都不是那么柔弱的女子\N不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.99,0:17:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.86,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒来命令我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令我坐下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  原谅姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不杀了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.94,0:17:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这一辈子恐怕都没有机会\N回到我身边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.94,0:17:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先杀了你\N然后跟你一起死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了从奈落手中把你抢回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对不能杀了琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.59,0:17:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要活着把他带回来才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.73,0:17:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会给大家添麻烦而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再咯里罗唆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正大家在一起就是比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.27,0:17:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也满会打架的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.55,0:18:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙到底在怕什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.82,0:18:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再打开风穴的话\N我会先折断你这只手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.79,0:18:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等到打败奈落\N风穴才能收起来对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是裹足不前的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的一点都没错  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要撑下去  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.95,0:18:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  看不出来\N你真有两下子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.46,0:18:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…身上好香啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候在说什么啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.61,0:19:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在人类的样子\N打不过他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.01,0:19:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会扔下你一个人跑掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.05,0:19:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.78,0:19:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.06,0:19:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  还有犬夜叉在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.83,0:19:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要还有犬夜叉在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那帮好朋友在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有再大的困难\N我们一定都能一起克服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.79,0:19:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才是我认识的你们嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马上可以\N离开这座森林了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口就在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚刚的一切\N都是蛾罗丸的幻术吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.33,0:20:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得我们无缘无故\N耽误了行程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  真的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.57,0:20:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.77,0:20:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过果然是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.41,0:20:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有我在一旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们根本就软弱到不行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.34,0:20:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  有什么不满吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  你说的并没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只限今天随便让你说说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.89,0:21:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.79,0:21:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了嘛  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都认同你够厉害\N不就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  这样我不接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们真的认为\N是我救了大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好歹跟我\N说一声“谢谢”才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样  戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.81,0:21:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦你\N代表大家说一句话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.18,0:21:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.58,0:21:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咿呀…你想干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.65,0:21:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来命令我坐下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.22,0:21:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.32,0:21:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.69,0:21:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢  谢  你  哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是过来叫我坐下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.13,0:21:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.73,0:21:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该继续上路咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.90,0:21:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.73,0:21:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我肚子饿了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.34,0:21:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  戈薇\N刚刚你跟我说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.14,0:21:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.34,0:21:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没关系  再说一次嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.84,0:21:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你烦不烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  喂  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.68,0:22:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  我在叫你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  给我坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.69,0:22:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.66,0:22:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.01,0:22:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.48,0:22:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.76,0:22:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.26,0:22:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.07,0:23:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.34,0:23:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默承受伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.85,0:23:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.52,0:23:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.86,0:23:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.29,0:23:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当年失去父亲之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.12,0:23:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有继续修行的年幼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.33,0:23:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天一直下着学\N学越积越多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.03,0:23:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个身子都被学淹没\N而动弹不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.06,0:23:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  就在那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.10,0:23:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位好心人救了我一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.47,0:23:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是七年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.47,0:23:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遇到的那位\N小学姑娘的经过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.27,0:23:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人\N跟我的救命恩人很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.67,0:24:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这场学\N也是你的眼泪凝结而成的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.08,0:24:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.61,0:24:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年之后\N一场令人怀念的大学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.91,0:24:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N这个女人根本就不是人类


